<%- include("templates/admin_header") %>


<div class="bg-gray-200 p-3">
    <div class="bg-gray-200 m-auto w-5/6 rounded-xl h-full">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 h-full items-center">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 grid-rows-1 md:grid-cols-2 mt-3">
                <div
                  class="mr-4 mt-3 block rounded-lg bg-white shadow-[0_2px_15px_-3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07),0_10px_20px_-2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h5
                        class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium leading-tight text-neutral-800">
                            Security Code
                        </h5>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-base text-neutral-600">
                            Change the security code needed to make an account. 
                        </p>
                        <form action="/generate-code" method="post" onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to generate a new code?');">
                            <span>Current Code</span>
                            <input type="text" id="code_display" value="<%= code %>" readonly>
                            <button type="submit" id="generate" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 border border-blue-700 rounded">Generate Code</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="mr-4 mt-3 block rounded-lg bg-white shadow-[0_2px_15px_-3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07),0_10px_20px_-2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h5
                        class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium leading-tight text-neutral-800">
                            Intake
                        </h5>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-base text-neutral-600">
                            Displays the current intake number.
                        </p>
                        <form action="/newIntake" method="post" onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to create a new Intake?');">
                            <span>Current Intake</span>
                            <input type="text" id="intake_display" value="<%= intake %>" readonly>
                            <button type="submit" id="generate" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 border border-blue-700 rounded">New Intake</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="mr-4 mt-3 block rounded-lg bg-white shadow-[0_2px_15px_-3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07),0_10px_20px_-2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h5
                        class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium leading-tight text-neutral-800">
                            Generate Lines 
                        </h5>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-base text-neutral-600">
                            Generate lines for the current intake. <br> <p style="color: red;">*Please update intake before creating new lines*</p> 
                        </p>
                        <form action="/generateSiteOptions" method="post" onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to generate new lines?');">
                            <button type="submit" id="generate" class="w-auto mt-3 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 border border-blue-700 rounded">Generate Lines</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                  class=" mt-3 block rounded-lg bg-white shadow-[0_2px_15px_-3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07),0_10px_20px_-2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h5
                        class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium leading-tight text-neutral-800">
                            Final Placement 
                        </h5>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-base text-neutral-600">
                            Assign current intake their placement.
                        </p>
                        <form action="/generate-pdf-final-placement" method="get" onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to assign students their final placements?');">
                            <button type="submit" id="generate" class="w-auto mt-3 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 border border-blue-700 rounded">Assign Practicum Placement</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                  class=" mt-3 block rounded-lg bg-white shadow-[0_2px_15px_-3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07),0_10px_20px_-2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h5
                        class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium leading-tight text-neutral-800">
                            Delete Account 
                        </h5>
                        <p class="mb-4 text-base text-neutral-600">
                            Delete a student account using their MRAD ID.
                        </p>
                        <form action="/delete-user" method="post" onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to delete this students account?');">
                            <input type="number" id="userMradId" name="userMradId">
                            <button type="submit" id="delete" class="w-auto mt-3 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 border border-blue-700 rounded">Delete Student</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class="block rounded-lg bg-white shadow-[0_2px_15px_-3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07),0_10px_20px_-2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)] w-3/4">
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h5
                    class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium leading-tight text-neutral-800">
                        Send Email
                    </h5>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-base text-neutral-600">
                        Send an email to all the students in INTAKE <%= intake %>
                    </p>
                    <form action="/admin/send-email" method="post" class="flex flex-col">
                        <textarea name="email_content" id="email_content" cols="30" rows="16" class="px-[20px] py-[12px] box-border resize-none border-solid border-2 rounded border-{#ccc} bg-{#f8f8f8}">Dear Student, 

The site placement process is now finalized. Based on your personal preferences and site popularity, the software has placed students in their clinical pathway for Term 2, 4 and 6. Note that Term 5 will be managed separately due to CT site capacity and variability.

While we recognize you may not have been placed at your preferred site(s), we hope that you will fully embrace the learning opportunities available at each short-term placement location to support your overall success in the program. In the event that the site placements are not acceptable, students have the option to withdraw from the program (for a partial refund less administrative fees) up until the withdrawal deadline: (insert date). It is the studentâ€™s responsibility to complete relevant withdrawal forms https://www.bcit.ca/files/pdf/admission/withdrawalft.pdf and communicate with the Medical Radiography Program Head, (insert name) (insert email) regarding withdrawal in a timely manner.

Please log into your site selector account (add link here) to view your clinical site placements.


Your clinical partners,
Caroline and Zahra</textarea>
                        <button type="submit" id="generate" class="w-96 mt-3 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 border border-blue-700 rounded">Send</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<%- include ("templates/footer") %>